PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773349953
OL,3,CNo apologies for devolved spending,
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer after leaked memo
OL,6,FSpeaking on Tuesday, Mr ap Iorwerth
OL,7,Ftold the Senedd: "There we have it in
OL,8,Fblack and white, Keir Starmer's own
OL,9,Fversion of Boris Johnson's muscular
OL,10,Funionism, not only dealing with
OL,11,Fdevolution in bad faith, but
OL,12,Fundertaking a direct assault on the
OL,13,Fdemocratic views of devolved
OL,14,Fgovernments.
OL,16,F"By staying ever loyal to him, the
OL,17,FFirst Minister (Eluned Morgan) is
OL,18,Faligning herself with efforts to
OL,19,Fundermine her own government.
OL,26,@oD@ROUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
