PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773349953
OL,3,CNo apologies for devolved spending,
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer after leaked memo
OL,6,F"Why has the Labour Party turned
OL,7,Fagainst devolution to this extent, and
OL,8,Fwhy has the First Minister allowed the
OL,9,FUK's Labour Prime Minister to treat
OL,10,Four Parliament, our government, and
OL,11,Fthe people of Wales with such
OL,12,Fcontempt?"
OL,14,FEluned Morgan said: "Devolution must
OL,15,Fbe respected, and I've always been
OL,16,Fvery clear with the Prime Minister on
OL,17,Fthat issue. It is a respectful
OL,18,Frelationship, and there are times, of
OL,19,Fcourse, when the UK Government should
OL,20,Fbe working directly within Wales."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]vD@UOU|D@bO]
