CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773349953
OL,3,CNo apologies for devolved spending,
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer after leaked memo
OL,6,FA No 10 source said: "We make no
OL,7,Fapologies for being determined to
OL,8,Fdeliver for people across all four
OL,9,Fnations of the UK. In Wales, Scotland
OL,10,Fand Northern Ireland, there are
OL,11,Fclearly reserved areas of governmental
OL,12,Fresponsibilities, and this government
OL,13,Fis committed to upholding this
OL,14,Fdevolution settlement with mutual
OL,15,Frespect and partnership."
OL,26,@nD@VOUwD@YO]
