OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773349953
OL,3,CNo apologies for devolved spending,
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer after leaked memo
OL,6,FAngus Robertson, Scotland's
OL,7,FConstitution Secretary and the SNP's
OL,8,Fcampaign manager for May's election,
OL,9,Faccused the Prime Minister of
OL,10,F"actively plotting to undermine our
OL,11,FParliament".
OL,13,FHe added: "The leaked memo is a
OL,14,Fdisturbing peak behind the curtain of
OL,15,Fa Westminster establishment that has
OL,16,Fabsolutely no respect for the national
OL,17,Fgovernments of these islands.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@KO]uD@KOU
