PN,46308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773349953
OL,3,CNo apologies for devolved spending,
OL,4,Csays Keir Starmer after leaked memo
OL,6,F"The reality is what this whole
OL,7,Fepisode has shown is that only through
OL,8,Fa fresh start with independence can
OL,9,Fthe integrity and future of Scotland's
OL,10,FParliament be protected and enhanced.
OL,12,F"Only the SNP is on the side of
OL,13,FScotland's Parliament, and this leaked
OL,14,Fmemo makes clear that only the SNP can
OL,15,Fbe trusted with the future of
OL,16,FHolyrood."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@JO]
